\subsubsection{Creation of an index for E. coli reference genome}

E. coli strain K12 fasa and gff3 were downloaded resp. with wget from \texttt{ftp://ftp.ensemblgenomes.org/pub/bacteria/release-36/fasta/bacteria\_0\_collection/escherichia\_coli\_str\_k\_12\_substr\_mg1655/dna/Escherichia\_coli\_str\_k\_12\_substr\_mg1655.ASM584v2.dna.chromosome.Chromosome.fa.gz} and \texttt{ftp://ftp.ensemblgenomes.org/pub/bacteria/release-36/gff3/bacteria\_0\_collection/escherichia\_coli\_str\_k\_12\_substr\_mg1655/Escherichia\_coli\_str\_k\_12\_substr\_mg1655.ASM584v2.36.gff3.gz} on 8th April 2017.

